d mention the positives:* The combat system is as good as EU's, just suffers from the ridiculous enemy progression/unbalance I mentioned* Much better mod support, including some mods to reduce/remove some of the negative points of the game* SO MUCH CHARACTER CUSTOMIZATION. If you loved XCOM for customizing your soldiers, you'll probably like 2 for this alone.This is a okay, but very flawed sequel. I didn't like this for the same reason I don't like Long War; what the devs consider challenging I just consider tedious and annoying."
