my favorite games and I can see myself coming back to it over time like I did Enemy Unknown. The challenging aspects of this game give you more of a sense of accomplishment after struggling through adversity and coming out on top and seeing the avatar project degrade or losing your core team and watching abuncha rookies pull you through a tough spot with the clutch.Rating for average gamer 8/10Rating for fan of xcom/strategy games 9/10 EASY!Its everything you love about Xcom refurbished and upgraded and expanded and streamlined with no DUMBING DOWN! A MUST BUY FOR STRATEGY OR XCOM FANS!"
