ake. and for the mentally insane and you people who just love to be punished you can even download the mod ""The Long War 2"" which is basically a free expansion imo, a free harder expansion.Talking about mods there are a ton, if you can imagine it it will probably be there. Want bob ross to be in your team?  No problem done! and the nicest thing is that the devs really support the modders talking in interviews over that the game really isn't theirs but just of the players and especially of the modders.Did i mention there will be new expansion in August?This game is gonna consume so much time of my life, i already feel it. hope it does for you too!"
