ven gender, other than what's selected.It's often far too difficult to click on specific tiles when targeting abilities like melee attacks and grenades.It seems like Vipers can grab you from literally across the map.You can have your engineers build ""experimental"" armor, weapons, grenades, and ammunition. This actually means that you throw away at least one elerium core and wait 7-30 days for a random item in that category that you may already have."
