ght consider this a good thing for a strategy game, but a lot of those times I felt like I had been cheated instead of outplayed-shot percentages feel like they are always way less than what they say (60% feels like 40%) maybe I'm just a ♥♥♥♥♥-some of the countdown missions feel way too rushed and next to impossible to come out with a success and a full crew. Then again that may have been the intention. ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥s.-Small bugs and glitches-long loading screens8/10"
