iers look goofy but thats all my opinion many people may like that kind of stuff but mods add better cosmetics so theres no real reason to buy it i have it because I bought the game if the year equvent of XCOM 2 so for me it was free but its not needed at all. anywho thats all for this review if you have any questions about the game I would be happy to answer them over all I would say for me this game is a 9/10 its amazing great controls never had a problem great graphics its well optomised and I haven't had one crash or even a frame rate drop."
