ll while aGIANT COUNTDOWN TO ARMAGEDDONis displayed to remind you that you have no chance in hell of stopping the enemy.Is that the point of this game? Is it really that nihilist? We are doomed no matter how successfully we play this life... the timer is forever against you? Why bother trying to win? Just revel in how much of your blood you can paint that building with.I WILL play this game again. And I WILL conquer this son of a ♥♥♥♥♥ someday. But the fact that it is such a chore to even think about playing, makes me so sad. How did they ruin such a great game?I'm sure I will receive copious amounts of ""lrn2play scrub"", but I simply cannot recommend this game. Even to fans of the very first brutal XCom: UFO Defense game. At least that game gave you a fighting chance if you played well.SCORE: 51/100May God have mercy on us all."
