ves you the option to replay it and was successful the second time around. Key: keep your squadmates close enough to provide overwatch fire but not to get♥♥♥♥♥♥♥by explosions.Game play value - 9/10 thus far. Its a fun game and I am definitely getting my $60 worth out of it. I can see infinite replay value out of it...like ALL XCOM games.Would I recommend it - damn straight! Its XCOM people. The world needs to be saved! ;-)"
